        "description": "The container closure system consists of a white HDPE bottle with a 2-piece child-resistant polypropylene closure containing a multi-layer aluminum foil induction seal with pulp liner for tamper evidence. The bottle and closure provide an adequate barrier to moisture and light, protecting the drug product. A reference-only paperboard carton is part of the marketed presentation but is excluded from the structured packaging hierarchy as secondary packaging is not within scope of the container closure system description.",
